value: 5093 - Scrap and Waste Materials Summary > TES-AMM AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover business services, not elsewhere classified. The company is involved in the export but not import of goods. TES-AMM AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is headquartered in Villawood, New South Wales. It is headed by director & company secretary Sharon Wendy Selwood. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $32.00 million. Its net loss totalled $1.12 million. TES-AMM AUSTRALIA PTY LTD forms part of the services industry sector.
